*How to use it?*
Install 'Greasemonkey':https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/748 Firefox Addon.
Restart Firefox for sure.
Click on 'arabicwikipedia.user.js':http://github.com/khaledalhourani/Arabic-Wikipedia-Font-Improvements 
from Firefox and Greasemonkey will install it as a user script.
Now Arabic Wikipedia is a lot easier to read!